</p>
<p>http://juris.ohchr.org 
</p>
<p>5. The following documents also contain information on the issues raised in Human 
</p>
<p>Rights Council resolution 9/8: </p>


<p>&#8226; Note by the Secretariat on timely, late and non-reporting by States parties to the 
</p>
<p>human rights treaty bodies (HRI/MC/2015/5) 
</p>
